d</a> by asking Alwaleed about his views on free speech.)</p><p style=3D"ma=
rgin: 16px 0;">Eventually Twitter=E2=80=99s board approved a merger at $54.=
20 per share. But last=C2=A0week, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/27652254.263132/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGd=
