important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-b=
ottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Musk announced</a> that Alwale=
ed will not be taking the $54.20. His Kingdom Holding Co.=C2=A0has agreed t=
o keep=C2=A0its shares and roll them over into=C2=A0the new, Musk-owned Twi=
tter. Incredibly, Elon Musk is finally going to take a public company priva=
te with <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27652254.2=
63132/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDgtM=
