li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You decide you are an all-around in=
vesting genius; you raise more money and expand your fund into other areas.=
</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Also you decide you are an all-ar=
ound=C2=A0<em>everything=C2=A0</em>genius and start telling corporate manag=
ers, politicians, teachers, scientists, etc., how to do their jobs.</li>=09=
<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Possibly you are wrong about one or both =
